When a young girl suddenly goes missing and local authorities are
unable to find her, a supernatural medium, familiar with such cases
of abduction steps in to save the day. Play as the role of Kim, a
spirit whisperer who must venture into the foul recesses of an
abandoned highland forest apartment where tragedy once struck. There
she must use all of her wits and tools at her disposal to break
through the spirit dimension in her search for the missing girl
